&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Research &amp;amp; Analysis&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct techno-economic analysis and literature reviews to support programme workstreams on low-emissions ammonia and fertiliser decarbonisation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the development of investment cases, market assessments, and pathway modelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Synthesise complex data and insights into clear, actionable outputs for both internal and external audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI and digital research tools to accelerate synthesis and insight generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
