&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Currently pursuing a degree in Engineering, Environmental Sciences, Agronomy, Public Administration, Economics, or related fields.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about sustainability issues (with a focus on climate, renewable energy, sustainable finance, food and land use systems transformation, circular economy, urban systems).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in English is mandatory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently and as part of a team.&lt;/li&gt;
