&lt;h2&gt;Role Overview&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We are seeking an Associate to join Systemiq&#39;s Nature &amp;amp; Food platform, supporting high-impact projects that accelerate the transition to more sustainable, resilient and inclusive food and land-use systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Working alongside colleagues across Europe and internationally, you will contribute to projects spanning regenerative agriculture, food systems transformation, biodiversity, land use, nature finance and sustainable value chains. You will help governments, businesses, financial institutions, philanthropies and civil society organisations develop practical, evidence-based solutions to complex sustainability challenges.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;This role is ideal for an early-career consultant or sustainability professional who enjoys structured problem-solving, research and stakeholder engagement, and is looking to develop rapidly within a collaborative and entrepreneurial consulting environment.&lt;/p&gt;
